					<div id="imCell_6" class="imGrid[2, 2]"><div id="imCellStyleGraphics_6"></div><div id="imCellStyle_6"><div id="imTextObject_6" style="text-align: left;"><div class="ff0 fs20"><p style="text-align: left;"><span class="ff1 cf3 fs24"><i>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr>-<wbr></i></span><i><span class="cf4 ff1 fs24"><b><br /></b></span></i><span class="ff2 cf4 fs24"><b><i>How to Get Red River Hostel</i></b></span><b><i><span class="ff1 cf4 fs24"> </span><span class="ff2 cf4 fs24">?</span></i></b><i><span class="cf5 ff2 fs24"><br /><br /><b>Map &amp; directions</b><br />To come to RED RIVER Hostel from Ataturk Airport, you may find your way to Taksim Tophane or Taksim Tunel<br /><br />1) Take the Subway from Ataturk Airport to Aksaray (Last Stop) .<br />When you come out of subway cross the main street towards to the Tramline and take the Tram from Yusufpasa Tram Stop to Tophane Station.<br /><br /></span></i><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24"><i>From Tophane station take the street calls Kumbaraci yokusu and climb the street like 100 meters after you will see </i></span><i><span class="ff1 cf5 fs24">Red River Hostel</span><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24"> on your left hand side we are No:35<br /></span></i><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24"><i><br />2.) You can get our from tram at Karakoy Station and you can take historical metro (calls Tunel) to get to the end point of Istiklal street.<br /><br /></i></span><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24"><i>After get in to Istiklal street if you will walk up about 150 meters on your right hand side you will see Kumbaraci Yokusu Street. Get in to Kumbaraci yokusu and walk 100 meters down on your right hand side you will find </i></span><i><span class="ff1 cf5 fs24">Red River Hostel</span><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24">.</span><span class="ff1 cf5 fs24"> </span><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24">Our building is No:35<br /></span></i><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24"><i><br />3.) Take a Public Bus nearby the Yusufpasa Tram Stop to Taksim Square<br />And than;<br /><br /></i></span><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24"><i>Walk into the Istiklal Street and just before end of the istiklal street after the Russian consulate turn left to (Kumbaraci Yokusu street) 100 m way down you will see </i></span><i><span class="ff1 cf5 fs24">Red River Hostel</span><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24"> on your right hand side.Our building is No:35<br /></span></i><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24"><i><br />4.) Take HAVAS bus from any airport to Taksim square<br />(There are 2 airports in Istanbul Sabiha Gokcen airport on the Asian side and Ataturk airport on the European side)<br />Than again,<br /><br /></i></span><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24"><i>Walk in to the Istiklal Street and just before end of the Istiklal Street after the Russian consulate turn left to (Kumbaraci Yokusu street) 100 m way down you will see</i></span><i><span class="ff1 cf5 fs24"> </span><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24">Red River Hostel on your right side.Our building is No:35<br /></span></i><span class="ff2 cf5 fs24"><i><br /><br />You ask for a Airport Pick-<wbr>up and we arrange it for you.</i></span><i><span class="ff1 cf5 fs24"><br /></span></i></p></div></div></div></div>
